PrecisAppointment of HOWARD BALLOCH as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, JACQUES BILODEAU as Ambassador of Canada to the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg, ALAIN DUDOIT as Ambassador of Canada to the Principality of Andorra, JEAN T. FOURNIER as High Commissioner for Canada in the Solomon Islands and Ambassador of Canada to the Federated States of Micronesia, ROBERT FOWLER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Albania and the Republic of San Marino, and as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Malta, and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the Food and Agriculture Organization, RAPHAËL GIRARD as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Moldova, MARGARET HUBER as Ambassador of Canada to the Slovak Republic, DONALD McMASTER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Liberia, MICHEL PERRAULT as Ambassador of Canada to the Central African Republic, LOUIS POISSON as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Sao Tomé and Principe, the Republic of Congo and the Republic of Equatorial Guinea, SANDELLE SCRIMSHAW as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Grenada, and PETER SUTHERLAND as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Nepal.
